Entries.default: "Land ho! Land ho!"
"That's no island! That be the Green Menace! We're doomed for sure!"
"Souls and gold and glory - you will give these to me!"
"For I am a god among gods and a true menace upon the seas!"
"Souls and gold and glory! Blame the Dawnstars, for they have summoned me."
"And now, I must feed!"
"'Twill be the end for us, it will! Oh, Ondra take me now!"
"Ladies and gentle-pirates - and rapscallions, too - you are in for the truest of mental treats!"
"And that's the story of how Eothas sank a fleet of our best tars."
"Without further ado, I present THE GREEN MENACE! Let us begin with our valiant new blood crews..."
"The Lusty Rudder and Fortune's Folly, two ships adrift at sea for weeks and weeks, on a venture most daring -"
"- in search... of the uncharted islands!"
"Woe and torture! Months at sea with no treasure to show for it!"
"You sure these uncharted islands exist, captain? We ain't seen land for days."
"Were they easy to find, they'd be called the charted islands, wouldn't they? If you're thinking to mutiny -"
"Got a lumpy looking island coming on the horizon!"
"Like the Floating Hangman, you see the Green Menace coming, you sail the other way."
"Thank you! Donations and gratuity are greatly appreciated."
"Come, one! Come, all!"
"Set your anchors lads for a performance of epic proportions!"
"Gather near, you fluttering doves! And pipe down, will you!"
"Gather closer for a tale of roiling adventure on the high seas!"
